<topic id="basex-support">
  <title>BaseX Database Connections</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Databases<indexterm>Connections<indexterm>BaseX</indexterm></indexterm></indexterm>
        <indexterm>BaseX database connection</indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p><ph keyref="product"/> includes support for BaseX database connections using a WebDAV
      connection. BaseX is a light-weight XML database engine and XQuery processor. <ph
        keyref="product"/> allows you to browse the structure of a BaseX database in the <xref
        href="relational-database-explorer.dita#relational-database-explorer"><uicontrol>Data Source
          Explorer</uicontrol> view</xref> and perform XQuery executions.</p>
  </body>
